{"tid":1763714,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"汽油彈同其他野 數目有無作大?","createTime":"2019-11-30T14:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T01:18:15.000Z","uid":291405,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b7153fd66b974c1d7cc8ef8e893e16d0ce94eb8c","tid":1763714,"uid":291405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T14:34:11.000Z","msg":"汽油彈同其他野 數目有無作大?<br />\n感覺幾百會有﹐幾千?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RwBzQ6X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRwBzQ6X.jpg&h=19b75e71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日行動共找到3801枚汽油彈，其中100枚綑綁了卡式手提氣罐，以增加殺傷力，並找到921支手提氣罐。警方亦檢獲558瓶化學品，包括強酸、強鹼、高腐蝕性液體及可造成炸藥的物品；另亦發現12把弓、自製弩、200支箭、1支氣槍、4箱用於刺穿車軚的釘，並拆除12個大型投擲器。停車場內有44輛車被破壞，包括打破油缸以取用汽油。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191128/s00001/1574901112530/%E3%80%901128-%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E3%80%91%E8%AD%A6%E6%90%9C%E7%8D%B23801%E6%9E%9A%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E5%85%A7%E8%A7%A3%E5%B0%81%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E6%92%A4%E9%9B%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191128%2Fs00001%2F1574901112530%2F%25E3%2580%25901128-%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2590%259C%25E7%258D%25B23801%25E6%259E%259A%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%25B0%2581%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2592%25A4%25E9%259B%25A2&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipfze9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=d934d134\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191128%2Fs00001%2F1574901112530%2F%25E3%2580%25901128-%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2590%259C%25E7%258D%25B23801%25E6%259E%259A%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%25B0%2581%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A